{"tid":2394145,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TRUMP前政府起訴耶魯大學收生疑「種族歧視亞裔美國人和白人」 拜登上任後撤告","createTime":"2021-02-04T03:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T07:37:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae8af3eaa4e6e5afc20b1ade38d749f8541f97a","tid":2394145,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"綜合外媒報導，川普前政府去年10月起訴耶魯大學，指控該大學在處理入學申請時，歧視白人和亞裔美國人，同時偏向黑人和西班牙裔，據美國司法部調查顯示，在學科成績相近的情況下，亞裔美國人和白人在耶魯大學的錄取率，通常只有非裔美國人的1/8到1/4，認定為「種族歧視」，違反1964年的《民權法案》。<br />\n<br />\n耶魯大學則回應，耶魯大學不會歧視任何種族的申請者，校方的招生作法完全公平且合法，相關政策不會因「毫無根據的訴訟」而改變。<br />\n<br />\n不過在拜登新政府上任後，決定撤銷對耶魯大學的訴訟，美司法部表示：「根據所有可知的事實、局勢和法律發展情況，決定撤回訴訟。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3431837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3431837&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRFmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=582cef35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3431837&h=aa6fc3ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3431837</a>"},{"pid":"9fe6309e77d0976c2c2f0c5124584fdf03dcbaf6","tid":2394145,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"511768a3ddd9379777bc72eefd7221db6d810ee3","tid":2394145,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"耶魯以後全部黑人教授"},{"pid":"8f3ff6b85281a69098749acd0d7a2fd7c18a611a","tid":2394145,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"511768a3ddd9379777bc72eefd7221db6d810ee3","tid":2394145,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"耶魯以後全部黑人教授"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"剩教體育"},{"pid":"7acfda1e4e08b4923f8a8ae15f5f0e45823c7a1b","tid":2394145,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"